[Course_Description]
Learn how to efficiently create, edit, and share presentations with PowerPoint 2019, the popular presentation platform. Instructor Jess Stratton kicks off the course by showing how to build a slideshow from scratch, as well as how to leverage PowerPoint templates and themes for quick construction. Jess then demonstrates how to add and edit text, images, charts, video, and animation; add speaker notes and transitions to ensure a smooth delivery; and actually present your polished slideshow. Plus, she steps through how to reuse and share your final presentation.